2026-05-12T16:37:43.4664368Z 13    <!--
2026-05-12T16:37:43.4664933Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-12T16:37:43.4665838Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
