2026-05-12T16:37:43.4674250Z 22    <!--
2026-05-12T16:37:43.4674808Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-12T16:37:43.4675534Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-12T16:37:43.4676379Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-12T16:37:43.4677186Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-12T16:37:43.4678007Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-12T16:37:43.4679039Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-12T16:37:43.4679902Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-12T16:37:43.4680763Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-12T16:37:43.4681596Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-12T16:37:43.4682390Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-12T16:37:43.4683032Z 33    -->
2026-05-12T16:37:43.4683653Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
