2026-05-12T16:37:43.4708304Z 46    <!--
2026-05-12T16:37:43.4708856Z 47        Foreground service used to keep the Pomodoro countdown alive when
2026-05-12T16:37:43.4709716Z 48        the app is backgrounded. Without this, a viewModelScope coroutine
2026-05-12T16:37:43.4710561Z 49        is cancelled as soon as the user switches apps and the completion
2026-05-12T16:37:43.4711378Z 50        notification is never shown. The timer is declared as a
2026-05-12T16:37:43.4712235Z 51        mediaPlayback foreground service because Samsung One UI suppresses
2026-05-12T16:37:43.4713423Z 52        FOREGROUND_SERVICE_SPECIAL_USE notifications, preventing the
2026-05-12T16:37:43.4714292Z 53        ongoing countdown notification from appearing on those devices.
